OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784051302
OL,3,CAmbulance service issues safety
OL,4,Cwarnings after busiest day on record
OL,5,Cin heatwave
OL,7,FThe South West's ambulance service has
OL,8,Fwarned people about staying safe in
OL,9,Fthe heat after it experienced its
OL,10,Fbusiest day on record one of the
OL,11,Fhottest days in June.
OL,13,FOn 25 June, South Western Ambulance
OL,14,FService NHS Trust (SWAST) received
OL,15,Fover 5,200 calls to its emergency
OL,16,Fcontrol rooms and handled more than
OL,17,F4,3000 incidents across the region,
OL,18,Fwhich was placed under a red heat
OL,19,Fhealth alert.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
