FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784051302
OL,3,CAmbulance service issues safety
OL,4,Cwarnings after busiest day on record
OL,5,Cin heatwave
OL,7,FJohn Martin, Chief Executive at SWAST,
OL,8,Fsaid: "We saw a real increase in
OL,9,Ffalls, those with breathing
OL,10,Fdifficulties, fainting - often because
OL,11,Fof heat exposure and being out in the
OL,12,Fsun too long."
OL,14,FThe service encourages people to only
OL,15,Fcall 999 if it's a life threatening
OL,16,Femergency or consider calling 111,
OL,17,Fspeaking with pharmacist, or attending
OL,18,Fa local minor injury unit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
