OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784051302
OL,3,CAmbulance service issues safety
OL,4,Cwarnings after busiest day on record
OL,5,Cin heatwave
OL,7,FThe South West has been placed under
OL,8,Fan amber heat health alert by the UK
OL,9,FHealth Security Agency (UKHSA) until
OL,10,FSunday (12 July) at 9pm BST, warning
OL,11,Fthat there's a greater risk to life
OL,12,Ffor vulnerable people.
OL,14,FThe UKHSA issue these alerts when
OL,15,Fthere's going to be a period of
OL,16,Fprolonged hot weather that's very
OL,17,Flikely to impact people and services.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784051302
OL,3,CAmbulance service issues safety
OL,4,Cwarnings after busiest day on record
OL,5,Cin heatwave
OL,7,F"You can really help out by making
OL,8,Fsure you don't end up in this
OL,9,Fsituation by staying hydrated, putting
OL,10,Fon suncream, staying out of heat in
OL,11,Fthe middle of the day."
OL,13,FThe SWAST chief advises that young
OL,14,Fchildren and the elderly are
OL,15,Fparticularly vulnerable during the
OL,16,Fheatwave.
OL,18,F"Young children and the elderly
OL,19,Fespecially need to stay cool and make
OL,20,Fsure they have access to cool water -
OL,21,Fso make sure to help them out".
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
