OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784051302
OL,3,CAmbulance service issues safety
OL,4,Cwarnings after busiest day on record
OL,5,Cin heatwave
OL,7,FHe says that some call-outs related to
OL,8,Felderly people who hadn't realised
OL,9,F"how hot (their) bodies are" and were
OL,10,Fwearing lots of clothes with the
OL,11,Fheating on inside their homes.
OL,13,FThe ambulance service saw twice as
OL,14,Fmany water-related and drowning
OL,15,Fincidents that they'd normally receive
OL,16,Fcompared to last year, with 50 water-
OL,17,Frelated incidents reported across a
OL,18,Fone-week period in June.
OL,26,@qD@JpmqD@Ppn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
