CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1784051302
OL,3,CAmbulance service issues safety
OL,4,Cwarnings after busiest day on record
OL,5,Cin heatwave
OL,7,F"Make sure to stay safe, go to
OL,8,Flifeguarded water and don't jump in
OL,9,Fwhere you can't see."
OL,26,@qD@UO]
